Singer 2Baba has responded to allegations of exploitation and consumption of hard drugs against his wife, Annie Idibia, by her elder brother Wisdom Macaulay. Wisdom Macaulay shocked many Nigerians with a video on Thursday morning where he accused his younger sister of shortchanging and introducing him to hard drugs. But the “African Queen” singer took to the comment section of the video to express his hurt. 2Baba noted his in-law’s post was a grievous one as it cuts deep into the soul.   You are a bloody liar, Annie Idibia replies elder brother     Marriage of Olu Jacobs’ son crashes     Annie Idibia exploited, introduced me to drugs, elder…   The music star hoped Macaulay would continue to stand by his post while sending him best wishes. “I understand people telling Annie not to respond. But this cuts deeps bro. “Dear Wisdom, I hope u are happy with this post. I hope u will continue to stand by this post. “Well, no matter what, it’s still nothing but best wishes and prayers for u from Annie and I. “Respect to family but sometimes, some family is your worst enemy,” he responded.